we'd really like the capability to create pseudo-columns in search results based on aggregate (i.e. "group by") functions. in particular, count/min/max/sum (std deviation would be cool too but not quite as necessary).  obviously count would work on any field grouped by, min/max would work on dates and numerics, sum would work on numerics only.

