  {panel}

It would be nice to have the ability to Export the Change Log or in that case any amount of data to XML.  I realize there is the ability to view the data in XML, but I cannot hook into this if the Project does not have "Anyone" under Browse Project and the project I want this information for is not set that way.  I tried saving the XML that was in the browser but it was just a blank file.

If you have:

String s = "Fix for issue TST-34\r\n";
GenericValue v[] = ServiceUtils.findIssuesInString(s);

Then v.length == 0.  problem is that the tokenizer will make the token be "TST-34\r".  '\r' needs to be added to the INVALID_ISSUEKEY_CHARS static.

